OL,3,CMajor investment in road where four
OL,4,Cpeople have died in the last five years
OL,6,FMore than half a million pounds will
OL,7,Fbe spent to prevent reckless and
OL,8,Fdangerous driving on a road in
OL,9,FHampshire, where four people have died
OL,10,Fin the last five years.
OL,12,F61 people have also been seriously
OL,13,Finjured on Portsdown Hill in that time.
OL,15,FWorks on the route north of
OL,16,FPortsmouth, will include average speed
OL,17,Fcameras, which the local authority
OL,18,Fhopes will help reduce speeding and
OL,19,Fimprove safety.
