OL,3,CMajor investment in road where four
OL,4,Cpeople have died in the last five years
OL,6,FHampshire's Police and Crime
OL,7,FCommissioner, Donna Jones, announced
OL,8,Fthe funding at a public meeting in
OL,9,FFarlington, saying: "I've listened to
OL,10,Fthe concerns of people living along
OL,11,FPortsdown Hill and the surrounding
OL,12,Fareas and I'm taking action.
OL,14,F"The majority of road users use that
OL,15,Froute safely, but a minority are
OL,16,Fmaking it increasingly hazardous and
OL,17,Fare putting lives at risk.
OL,19,F"There have been 61 injury incidents
OL,20,Fover the past five years. It's one of
OL,21,Fthe most dangerous roads in Hampshire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
