OL,3,CMajor investment in road where four
OL,4,Cpeople have died in the last five years
OL,6,F"Other preventative measures in the
OL,7,Farea will also be considered. The
OL,8,Fnoise pollution caused by motorbikes
OL,9,Fand cars is also proving unbearable
OL,10,Fand blights the lives of thousands of
OL,11,Fpeople.
OL,13,F"This behaviour is unacceptable and
OL,14,Fcan't go on."
OL,16,FPortsmouth City Council as well as
OL,17,FHampshire and Isle of Wight
OL,18,FConstabulary will partner with the
OL,19,FPolice and Crime Commissioner to
OL,20,Fdeliver the improvement works.
